<meta name="assert" content="The 'context-menu' cursor value is supported">
<style><meta>The test passes if, when moved inside the blue box, the cursor indicates availability of a context menu.
  Often rendered as an arrow with a small menu-like graphic next to it.</style>
<body>
  <meta><p><style>
div {
  cursor: url("support/cursors/fail.png"), help;
  cursor: context-menu;
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  border: solid blue;
}
</style></p><body>
